race.comment: FIORENTE DE LEGEND (6) has been freshened following a plain run over 1650m at Devonport Synthetic. Much better suited back in trip and on the turf. Her last two outings here stack right up for this. Draws inside today and the 3kg claim is handy. GEEGEEHAILSTORM (7) just missed in a CL2 and will be better for it. Has to manage a wide gate but keeps the premier hoop and has more to give. NO ACCESS (10) also draws awkwardly but improved again, narrowly beaten in a 60 just 8 days ago. He can make the finish with average luck. RUBBLEONTHEDOUBLE (2) has been freshened off synthetic runs in a bit stronger. He has ability, and the 3kg claim brings him into it to an extent.
